x4freetext: Each stack consisted of natural Eu(2)O(3) sedimented
targets, several aluminum absorber and catcher foils.
prepared by sedimentation of natural Eu(2)O(3) powder
from an ethanolic suspension onto aluminum backings of
15 mm diameter and 50 mum thickness. For protection the
sediments were covered with aluminum foils of 10 mum
Pellets of europium oxide for thick-target yields were
prepared by pressing the powder in a cylindrical
molding with a diameter of 10 mm.
